    "prompt": "Construct a program which determines whether the original string is a palindrome. The function should be case insensitive i.e. upper and lowercase letters are intepreted as being the same.",
    "source_code": "str = \"Madam\"\nn_str = str.lower()\nrevers_str = \"\"\nfor char in n_str:\n    revers_str = char + revers_str\nif n_str == revers_str:\n    print(\"This string is a palindrome!\")\nelse:\n    print(\"The string is not a palindrome!\")"
